      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "# ⭐ Krea 2 — High Quality ⭐ StarNodes Template\n\n**Pipeline:** ① Load Krea 2 models ➜ ② Prompt (optional Ollama refiner) ➜ ③ Size & sample ➜ ④ SeedVR2 upscale ➜ ⑤ Refine & save\n**Requires:** ComfyUI 0.25+ · StarNodes · WAS Node Suite · (optional) Ollama running locally for the prompt helper"
      ],
      "color": "#223",
      "bgcolor": "#335"
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [
        100,
        300
      ],
      "size": [
        480,
        210
      ],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 6,
      "mode": 0,
      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "properties": {
        "Node name for S&R": "Note"
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "**ℹ️ Group notes**\n• **Load Diffusion Model** — the Krea 2 checkpoint (Turbo FP8 recommended).\n• **Load CLIP** — Qwen3VL-4B text encoder, keep type **krea2**.\n• **Load VAE** — Qwen-Image VAE used by Krea 2.\n• **Lora Loader** — optional style/character LoRA on top of the base model.\n• **Star Krea2 Unbound** — StarNodes patch that lets the Krea 2 model answer the prompt freely, without its built-in boundaries."
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [
        720,
        300
      ],
      "size": [
        440,
        210
      ],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 7,
      "mode": 0,
      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "properties": {
        "Node name for S&R": "Note"
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "**ℹ️ Group notes**\n• **Star Ollama Prompt Helper** — turns a short idea into a rich Krea 2 prompt using a local Ollama LLM (server + model selectable). Skip it and type directly into CLIP Text Encode if you prefer.\n• **Preview Any** — shows the refined prompt text before encoding.\n• **CLIP Text Encode** — encodes the final prompt into conditioning."
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
